### Complete Lean 4 Proof without `sorry`

```lean
theorem map_comp {α β : Type*} [C : Category α] [D : Category β]
  (F : α → β) (homF : ∀ {X Y : α}, C.Hom X Y → D.Hom (F X) (F Y))
  (map_id : ∀ (X : α), homF (id X) = id (F X))
  (map_comp : ∀ {X Y Z : α} (f : C.Hom X Y) (g : C.Hom Y Z), homF (g ≫ f) = homF g ≫ homF f)
  (f g : α → α) (h : ∀ (X : α), f X = g X) : ∀ (X : α), homF (f X) = homF (g X) := by
  intro X
  have h₁ : f X = g X := h X
  rw [h₁]
  <;>
  simp_all
  <;>
  aesop
```
